dating always leads to marriage.

309
00:28:29,360 --> 00:28:31,570
But that's not quite true
for kids nowadays, right?

310
00:28:31,570 --> 00:28:35,200
They may do some crazy stuff together,
but that's irrelevant to marriage.

311
00:28:35,200 --> 00:28:39,880
