I'm sorry for being old-fashioned.

318
00:29:03,290 --> 00:29:06,140
If she introduces you to
the elders at a family event

319
00:29:06,140 --> 00:29:07,700
it means you two will get married.

320
00:29:07,700 --> 00:29:10,550
If you tell people you two have
broken up after that

321
00:29:10,550 --> 00:29:12,650
it's equivalent to
breaking a marriage off.

322
00:29:12,650 --> 00:29:14,570
That's how the elders will take it.

323
00:29:14,570 --> 00:29:18,300
Even if she asks you to just come to
the wedding and grab a meal...

324
00:29:19,380 --> 00:29:22,090
you can't come to it
with that same mindset.

325
00:29:22,090 --> 00:29:25,290
If you're determined that you'll
marry Hae Young no matter what

326
00:29:25,290 --> 00:29:28,730
then you can come tomorrow.
If not, don't come.

327
00:29:28,730 --> 00:29:32,260
If there is even the slightest thing
stopping you, don't come.

328
00:29:36,810 --> 00:29:41,060
Hae Young's marriage
has been ruined once.

329
00:29:41,060 --> 00:29:44,420
I can't just stand and watch
another one get ruined like that.

330
00:29:58,390 --> 00:30:00,610
What did he say?

331
00:30:01,700 --> 00:30:03,650
He's not the one.

332
00:30:22,000 --> 00:30:25,100
<i>[Hae Young]</i>

333
00:30:31,250 --> 00:30:34,290
- Hey.
<i>- Why did you take so long to answer?</i>

334
00:30:34,290 --> 00:30:38,380
- I was showering.
- You were showering?

335
00:30:41,750 --> 00:30:44,800
Sorry. What are you doing tomorrow?

336
00:30:45,960 --> 00:30:48,110
I'm going to the countryside for work.
I'll be back in the afternoon.

337
00:30:48,110 --> 00:30:49,970
Is that so?

338
00:30:49,970 --> 00:30:53,050
I'm going to my cousin's
wedding tomorrow.

339
00:30:54,040 --> 00:30:56,980
I'll see you at my house tomorrow
evening. I'll cook you something good.

340
00:30:56,980 --> 00:31:00,540
