341
00:31:00,540 --> 00:31:03,570
I'm good at it.
Don't eat too much at the wedding.

342
00:31:04,300 --> 00:31:05,900
All right. I've got it.

343
00:31:05,900 --> 00:31:08,300
- What do you like to eat?
<i>- Everything.</i>

344
00:31:08,300 --> 00:31:11,530
<i>I don't particularly hate
or love any type of food.</i>

345
00:31:11,530 --> 00:31:13,920
Should we get a drink tomorrow too?

346
00:31:13,920 --> 00:31:16,290
<i>I think it's been forever
since I've had a drink.</i>

347
00:31:16,290 --> 00:31:18,350
I think it's been over 10 days.

348
00:31:20,330 --> 00:31:23,870
I've figured out why
I had been drinking so much.

349
00:31:23,870 --> 00:31:26,620
It was because I wasn't happy.

350
00:31:26,620 --> 00:31:30,560
Nowadays, I feel happy
all the time as if I'm drunk.

351
00:31:32,160 --> 00:31:35,030
- Thank you.
- I'm more grateful.

352
00:31:42,890 --> 00:31:44,820
Oh my god!

353
00:31:44,820 --> 00:31:47,280
Why aren't you in bed?

354
00:31:51,690 --> 00:31:53,800
Don't worry about tomorrow.

355
00:31:53,800 --> 00:31:57,210
He can't come to the wedding anyway.
He has to work.

356
00:32:27,940 --> 00:32:29,750
Are you looking for me?

357
00:32:31,030 --> 00:32:32,390
Oh my god!

358
00:32:32,390 --> 00:32:35,300
- Are you ready?
- No. I mean...

359
00:32:35,300 --> 00:32:38,840
- Should we kiss?
- It's just that I have... You know...

360
00:32:38,840 --> 00:32:42,530
It's not like that. No. Absolutely not.

361
00:32:51,190 --> 00:32:53,850
Tell me when you're ready.

362
00:32:53,850 --> 00:32:55,980
If you lack the confidence,
then give up.

363
00:33:04,740 --> 00:33:06,700
