372
00:33:54,530 --> 00:33:58,580
- She didn't get married that time.
- So she's going to marry that guy again?

373
00:33:59,970 --> 00:34:04,180
Mother, I'll tell you about everything
in detail when we get home.

374
00:34:08,510 --> 00:34:10,120
Is she going to have another wedding?

375
00:34:10,120 --> 00:34:12,640
I will tell you later.

376
00:34:12,640 --> 00:34:14,390
We will do it one more time.

377
00:34:14,390 --> 00:34:18,140
This time, throw it gently.

378
00:34:18,140 --> 00:34:20,950
Ready? Throw it.

379
00:34:47,260 --> 00:34:49,300
It was salty.
All buffets makes me thirsty.

380
00:34:49,300 --> 00:34:51,580
- Here.
- I'm okay.

381
00:34:52,060 --> 00:34:55,930
I haven't seen a very beautiful bride
yet at wedding halls.

382
00:34:55,930 --> 00:34:58,950
I tell them
they're beautiful as a courtesy.

383
00:34:58,950 --> 00:35:00,830
If someone tells me that
I'm pretty at my wedding

384
00:35:00,830 --> 00:35:03,350
I will never be fooled.

385
00:35:13,780 --> 00:35:16,080
Why did you come along?
You should've stayed home.

386
00:35:16,080 --> 00:35:20,140
She's at home, you know.

387
00:35:20,560 --> 00:35:22,620
Don't take too much time.
Make a decision.

388
00:35:22,620 --> 00:35:24,550
Whatever decision you make

389
00:35:24,550 --> 00:35:26,550
my sister or I won't resent you.

390
00:35:26,550 --> 00:35:30,810
Do Kyung, can you
possibly kiss your sister?

391
00:35:30,970 --> 00:35:33,950
