I need to do something.

396
00:35:43,470 --> 00:35:46,850
Gosh, I really don't know what to do.

397
00:35:56,260 --> 00:35:59,890
What is it? Are you going to
cook for Oh Hae Young Two?

398
00:35:59,890 --> 00:36:01,930
