432
00:38:01,410 --> 00:38:02,890
Are you ready?

433
00:38:03,410 --> 00:38:05,160
Shall we kiss?

434
00:38:06,490 --> 00:38:08,640
When you're ready, tell me.

435
00:38:09,970 --> 00:38:11,660
Get out of my way!

436
00:38:23,560 --> 00:38:26,890
