after you ask me?

457
00:39:45,120 --> 00:39:46,780
That's pretty.

458
00:39:51,810 --> 00:39:53,950
I'm so happy!

459
00:40:02,280 --> 00:40:04,300
Soo Kyung.

460
00:40:05,660 --> 00:40:08,370
