- Okay.

482
00:42:16,610 --> 00:42:18,580
Ta-da!

483
00:42:18,580 --> 00:42:21,750
This is a letter for me
written by a high school boy.

484
00:42:21,750 --> 00:42:23,000
It's so cute.

485
00:42:23,000 --> 00:42:25,100
