through my letters today.

486
00:42:25,100 --> 00:42:27,290
He's so cute. Listen to this.

487
00:42:27,290 --> 00:42:28,790
I won't get jealous
of a high school boy, okay?

488
00:42:28,830 --> 00:42:31,170
Just listen to this.

489
00:42:31,790 --> 00:42:35,350
