my heart also broke down."

491
00:42:39,110 --> 00:42:41,250
"I wanted to comfort you."

492
00:42:41,250 --> 00:42:43,860
"But I couldn't interrupt
while you were crying."

493
00:42:43,860 --> 00:42:46,900
"I just followed behind you."

494
00:42:46,900 --> 00:42:50,150
"If you happened to collapse from crying"

495
00:42:50,170 --> 00:42:52,500
